OL,3,CContaminated Blood: The Hampshire
OL,4,Cschool where dozens of pupils died
OL,6,FSpecial video report by ITV News
OL,7,FMeridian's Rachel Hepworth.
OL,9,FEvery story of infected blood is
OL,10,Fshocking.
OL,12,FBut what happened to pupils at
OL,13,FTreloar's School in Hampshire has been
OL,14,Fdescribed as a tragedy within a
OL,15,Ftragedy.
OL,17,FThe college in Alton was meant to be a
OL,18,Fhaven for haemophiliac boys who might
OL,19,Fbe at risk in the outside world.
