OL,6,FAde Goodyear describes the shock of
OL,7,Fbeing told he was infected with HIV
OL,9,FWHAT IS HAEMOPHILIA?
OL,11,FIt is a rare genetic condition in
OL,12,Fwhich the blood does not clot
OL,13,Fproperly. It mostly affects men but is
OL,14,Fpassed through the female line.
OL,16,FPeople with the condition produce
OL,17,Flower amounts of the essential blood-
OL,18,Fclotting protein known as factor VIII
OL,19,Fand IX.
