OL,6,F"Someone came along and said look
OL,7,Fguys, rather than you having to go to
OL,8,Fhospital and hold your arm out and be
OL,9,Fthere overnight for a long
OL,10,Ftransfusion, you're going to have a
OL,11,F60mil syringe that's going to take 10
OL,12,Fminutes to give yourself and then you
OL,13,Fcan go back out and play football, and
OL,14,Fbasically, what nine or 10 year old is
OL,15,Fnot going to say 'yep- I'll have that'"
