OL,6,FWhat they didn't know was that Factor
OL,7,F8 was, in some cases, made from blood
OL,8,Fdonated by groups at high risk of HIV
OL,9,Fand hepatitis, including drug addicts
OL,10,Fand prisoners in America, paid for
OL,11,Ftheir donation.
