OL,6,FLee met his future wife while they
OL,7,Fwere pupils at Treloars. She sadly
OL,8,Fdied in the early 2000s. His return to
OL,9,FTreloars today is the first time he
OL,10,Fhas felt able to come.
OL,12,FThe day is emotional for all of them.
OL,13,FWe are here at the invitation of
OL,14,FTreloars, a chance for the former
OL,15,Fstudents to remember the friends they
OL,16,Flost.
