OL,6,FAnother of the group, Richard Warwick,
OL,7,F55, from Scarborough, says the
OL,8,Frepercussions are lifelong: "There is
OL,9,Fanother burden, and that is of
OL,10,Fsurvivor's guilt- because we have lost
OL,11,Fso many school friends, people who we
OL,12,Fthought were untouchables at the time-
OL,13,F and that is a very hard pill to
OL,14,Fswallow"
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/18
