OL,6,F"My parents were kept completely in
OL,7,Fthe dark," says Gary. "I got letters
OL,8,Fhome from the school telling them I'd
OL,9,Fbeen a naughty boy, but nothing about
OL,10,Fmy treatment, or my illnesses. Nothing
OL,11,Ffor eight years."
OL,13,FHe only learned during the inquiry
OL,14,Fthat he had been put on a trial during
OL,15,Fhis first year at school.
OL,17,FIts former headmaster, Alec
OL,18,FMacpherson, told the inquiry he had
OL,19,Fknown about the research but avoided
OL,20,Fquestioning the doctors because he
OL,21,Ftrusted them.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/18
