OL,6,FFollowing that evidence, Gary moved to
OL,7,Fsue the school for breaching its duty
OL,8,Fof care.
OL,10,FHis court case is on hold pending the
OL,11,Freport findings.
OL,13,FIn a statement, Treloar's said;
OL,14,F"Staff, students and their families,
OL,15,Ftogether placed their trust in the
OL,16,Ftreatment and advice given out by the
OL,17,FNHS clinic, and the doctors and
OL,18,Fmedical professionals who ran it in
OL,19,Fthe 1970s and 80s.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G15/18
