OL,6,F"It has been shocking to discover,
OL,7,Fthrough the ongoing public inquiry,
OL,8,Fthat some of our students may have
OL,9,Freceived treatment there which was
OL,10,Funsafe or experimental, and that the
OL,11,FNHS did not always obtain sufficient
OL,12,Fconsent.
OL,14,FWe know that people's lives were torn
OL,15,Fapart by what was done to them, right
OL,16,Facross the country, through the
OL,17,Ftreatment they received from the NHS
OL,18,Fat the time.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G16/18
