OL,6,F"They all deserve answers from the
OL,7,Fongoing public inquiry, and we
OL,8,Fstrongly support the urgent need to
OL,9,Faccelerate compensation payments from
OL,10,Fthe Government. We want to ensure that
OL,11,Ftheir horrendous experiences are
OL,12,Facknowledged and remembered."
OL,14,FNow, as the report is published, the
OL,15,FTreloars boys say they've honoured the
OL,16,Fpledge they made to their classmates:
