OL,6,F"There's all the people who should be
OL,7,Fhere" says Ade. "They should be and
OL,8,Fthey're not. It's a lot of
OL,9,Fresponsibility for us to carry and for
OL,10,Ftheir families.
OL,12,F"There are people now hiding away so
OL,13,Fwe have to speak up and treasure their
OL,14,Fmemory and make sure that we carry it
OL,15,Fas best as we can."
